replies.body:
Hey there,

That's a placeholder name being displayed due to the [current issue affecting the visibility of ward skins.](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/224867827--August-9-We-re-aware-of-an-issue-where-some-ward-skins-don-t-appear-or-prevent-the-ward-skin-selection-box-from-appearing-)

If you make the ward skin permanent, it will not display on your profile or in the ward skin selector, however the ward skin is in your "inventory" and will be visible as soon as the issue is resolved.
